divs: Sighting Detailswhile vacationing in mackinac memorial weekend 2008 we were at the mackinac point lighthouse immediatly east of the bridge. i took a couple of pics of the bridge. when reviewing the pics i noticed one of them had spot. i have no idea what it is but i am confident it is not dirt, a bird, a plane or anything else known.
